The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Chandhok shines
                                                   Chandhok shines
                      
	Chennai: Indias Karun Chandhok set the Paul Ricard track in France ablaze, finishing first and fourth, respectively, in tricky weather conditions in the two test sessions of his new iSport international car on Thursday, an iSport release said .         
	Chandhok lapped the circuit in 1:12.717s, nearly a tenth of a second clear of second-placed Piquet driver Pastor Maldonado and the current GP2 leader Romain Grosjean, who finished third. (PTI)                                                                                                                       
